  "detailed_description": "<h1>Become a Burger Chef!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310020/extras/a176985c8aab3d3f6596e32dd5a4a049.avif?t=1772361310\" width=600 height=190 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In Top Burger Shop, whip up delicious burgers to satisfy hungry customers in a vibrant, fast-paced environment! Manage your shop, unlock new ingredients, and navigate fun challenges across 180 levels. Are you ready to delight your patrons?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310020/extras/71358c5585505f4eb33c32965688cae4.webp?t=1772361310\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310020/extras/ba54371c94caed3022a912038b249eb8.poster.avif?t=1772361310\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310020/extras/ba54371c94caed3022a912038b249eb8.webm?t=1772361310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310020/extras/ba54371c94caed3022a912038b249eb8.mp4?t=1772361310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Top Burger Shop</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Top Burger Shop Simulator, become a master burger chef, crafting delicious food items to satisfy hungry customers. Manage your shop while unlocking new ingredients and characters, and take on fun challenges that test your culinary skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310020/extras/934f193dd1392b47c2cb57e9760da5a9.webp?t=1772361310\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310020/extras/75737d2c62f48155ee80a9a733c8b808.poster.avif?t=1772361310\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310020/extras/75737d2c62f48155ee80a9a733c8b808.webm?t=1772361310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310020/extras/75737d2c62f48155ee80a9a733c8b808.mp4?t=1772361310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore three worlds with unique challenges across 180 levels. Utilize exciting power-ups: Auto-hint, Coin Magnet, and Customer Happy Time. Choose from 21 charming animated characters and unlock new ingredients and power-ups as you progress. Enjoy three game modes—Chef Championship, Career, and Time Attack—for a tasty journey!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In Top Burger Shop, whip up delicious burgers to satisfy hungry customers in a vibrant, fast-paced environment! Manage your shop, unlock new ingredients, and navigate fun challenges across 180 levels. Are you ready to delight your patrons?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310020/extras/71358c5585505f4eb33c32965688cae4.webp?t=1772361310\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310020/extras/ba54371c94caed3022a912038b249eb8.poster.avif?t=1772361310\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310020/extras/ba54371c94caed3022a912038b249eb8.webm?t=1772361310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310020/extras/ba54371c94caed3022a912038b249eb8.mp4?t=1772361310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Top Burger Shop</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Top Burger Shop Simulator, become a master burger chef, crafting delicious food items to satisfy hungry customers. Manage your shop while unlocking new ingredients and characters, and take on fun challenges that test your culinary skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310020/extras/934f193dd1392b47c2cb57e9760da5a9.webp?t=1772361310\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/sto